     <br>
Name: Escape <br>
Level Requirement: 59 <br>
Ability Type: Activated  <br>
Re-Use Time: 1 hour 12 minutes <br>
Max Training: 1 Levels <br>
Point Cost: 9 <br>
Description: This ability allows the rogue to completely hide from the an opponent, even one actively seeking them out.<br>
When escape is used the Rogue is removed from all hate lists of all enemies.<br>
<br>
If the Rogue is not in combat when this skill is used they will also immediately 'hide'.<br>
<br>
The refresh timer for this skill is 72 minutes. It is incredibly useful for those fights where the Rogue over-aggros and cannot shake the enemy even with evades.<br>
